You can fully recover HP and MP. Would you like to fully
recover?
全探索者のスイッチ初期化
全探索者の強制ロスト

This is an event you have already seen. Would you like to
skip the pre-battle sequence?
What in the world is going on here!?

Heh heh heh, these guys turned out to be less useful than I
thought, so I'm just making use of them as spirit power
tanks at least.
Magical power tanks... What do you think our comrades are!!

Comrades...? To me, comrades are only about whether they're
useful or not... That's all.

You've been gathering spirit power to operate that "Ogre,"
haven't you?

If that's the case, it's meaningless for you to gather
spirit power anymore because I've already destroyed it!

Ah... that's true... I never expected you to be able to
destroy it on your own... I must admit I'm surprised...

But... thanks to you, it's been proven that the "Ogre" has
enough combat power to corner the "Guardians' Ace."

It was certainly tough, but thinking one alone could
annihilate the Guardians is too naive, isn't it?
Heh heh heh... Who said there was only one "Ogre"?
イベントへスクロール
イベントへスクロール
There are so many of them...

The spirit power you've absorbed since you infiltrated here
has been used as food for these guys!
...So you let me go on purpose... to get my power.
That's right, your power has been very useful to me!
イベントへスクロール
イベントへスクロール
Hisana-chan, sorry to keep you waiting! I've arrived!

That is the \c[2]Leviathan\c[0]!! To think you'd bring out
such a thing...

I did say that we probably didn't need to bring out the
Guardians' flagship...

But from what I've heard, it seems like it was the right
decision. Did you foresee this much?

...Wait a minute... If "Leviathan" is here, then Hisana-chan
and... could it be... those people are with her...

Heh heh heh, it's an honor to have the Guardians' main force
come to us.

However, they probably didn't expect us to have this much
firepower.

Now, my "Ogres," show those self-righteous hypocrites your
power!
イベントへスクロール

Be careful! There are so many "Ogres" heading your way!
Don't worry, those two are coming out!
イベントへスクロール
イベントへスクロール

Im... impossible... All those "Ogres" wiped out in an
instant...!?
Well yeah... if those two show up... that's what happens.

Even so, I never imagined that \c[2]Mom\c[0] and the others
would come.
I have some sad news for Kohane-chan here.
No! I don't want to hear it!

Those two went off on their own and are also quite angry
with Kohane-chan who ran ahead recklessly.
"Hurry up and finish this and come back," is what they said.
Uuu... I'm scared to go back...

That power... the power of the \c[2]legendary twins\c[0]...
Don't mess with me... What the hell is that...
It seems like his spirit is broken too...

All the preparations I've made... in an instant... Damn it,
damn it, damn damn damn!

Now that it's come to this, I'll defeat you, take you
hostage, and make them listen to me.

But it won't be that easy, so I'll have to use my trump
card!

The spiritual power collected from others can be used as
energy for spiritual power weapons, but it can't be used
directly by others... however...

Thanks to the experiments here, those who don special
equipment can temporarily handle the collected spiritual
power!

Relax, I'll use your body and spiritual power all for
myself!
My body and spiritual power are mine!

I'll absolutely, definitely send you flying to the ends of
the stars!!

Gah...ugh... Even with the power of the Liberators combined,
it's not enough...
So this is... the power of a magical girl of justice...
I don't know if I'm truly just or not.

But using the "power" I was born with to take away people's
happiness is wrong.

That's why I use this "power" to create a world where
everyone can live happily.

Ha, I couldn't care less about others! I just sought a world
where I could live feeling good.

But this time, your "power" of belief was stronger than the
"power" I sought.

However, don't forget... even if you've defeated us, there
are still Liberators around the world who share our cause!

I'll be looking forward to seeing if you can protect the
world while sticking to your "righteousness"!
Enjoy your fleeting moments of playing the hero of justice!

It must be the backlash from gathering other people's
spiritual power... It's not easy to handle someone else's
spiritual power...

I see... But if this research progresses further... it's
kind of scary.

Right, and there are still more Liberators out there, aren't
there?

They were quite tough... and to think there are still
others...
Oh my, Kohane-chan is unusually humble.

No way! I'm just thinking that I need to psych myself up
again!

So when we get back, we'll have to train together, Hisana-
chan!
Before that, you're in for a proper scolding...!
Right, we have to rescue Amy and the others!

And so, my "meticulously calculated undercover
investigation" thwarted the Liberators' plans.

When Hisana-chan and the others who rushed over
investigated, they found out that this lab was connected to
other Liberator organizations and sharing experimental
results.

That robot named "Ogre" was apparently going to be delivered
to organizations all over the world too.

The Guardians will have to face these Liberator
organizations around the world from now on... so we have to
stay sharp and keep at it...
To continue the story a bit...
Amy-chan became an apprentice under the Guardians' care.

She was originally tricked into joining them, so it seems
she'll be treated like she's under "protective observation?"
She follows me everywhere and it's really cute.
She must have been lonely all this time...

For me, it's like having a little sister and I'm really
happy about it!

The other Liberators, though, had committed too many crimes
and were sent to a special facility...

They don't answer any questions about the other Liberators.
It's not going to be that easy, huh.

But... someday... I hope they use their power to protect
people's happiness.

I got a severe scolding from my parents for running off on
my own.

Hisana-chan was angry too, but... she quickly started crying
and hugged me.

"When the communication cut off, I was really scared you'd
never come back..." she said.

At that time, I thought I was done for... but I managed to
keep going because I knew Hisana-chan was waiting for me.

But since I've caused so much worry... I'll "behave myself"
for a while. Yeah.

And so, as a member of the Guardians once again, I devoted
myself to the activities of a magical girl, to protect
everyone's happiness.
Suddenly, everything in front of me turned white...
[EX]セルフスイッチタイプ = A
